{"tid":48485,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"碧咸細仔Cruz搵家人助陣拍MV 哈七好活潑","createTime":"2016-12-21T06:01:04.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-21T06:23:00.000Z","uid":19502,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"32c2ab57d3730c055f6fd68c30bd22b71e209d33","tid":48485,"uid":19502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:01:04.000Z","msg":"英國萬人迷碧咸（David Beckham）嘅11歲細仔Cruz，進軍歌壇推出首支聖誕單曲《If Everyday Was Christmas》，收益會捐畀慈善團體，歌曲MV已經公開，Cruz搵咗家人助陣，幫佢製作咗一個充滿溫情嘅MV。<br />\n<br />\nCruz喺MV開首對住鏡頭擺Chok、喺落住人造雪同閃粉嘅環境下獻唱，MV仲播放Cruz同兩位阿哥Brooklyn與Romeo，以及細妹哈七（Harper Seven）喺倫敦生活嘅片段。見到佢哋幾兄弟喺度踩板，Cruz亦都拖住哈七踩Roller，佢哋幾個感情好好，Cruz又整蠱Brooklyn同Romeo，將啲糖照頭淋落佢哋個頭度，之後仲互相掟樹葉，連哈七同老竇碧咸都掟埋一份，哈七真係好活潑，不過就唔見媽咪Victoria有喺MV出現。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/21/135919_31b622b471eec25b99ab3f377e7c5072.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F21%2F135919_31b622b471eec25b99ab3f377e7c5072.jpg&h=79f78c36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lnQXO342N7w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlnQXO342N7w&d=vzobyLwFp2vGH3L1F%2B0ji38C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=67cf528e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lnQXO342N7w</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20161217/56059032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20161217%2F56059032&d=vzobyLwFp2vGH3L1F%2B0ji38C1RzHckko4WZAlj2iIrY%3D&h=53560993\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20161217%2F56059032&h=382cc070\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20161217/56059032</a>"},{"pid":"aec74e00e84a6fcc7989670aad77a642a68db10d","tid":48485,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪想行will smith 條路？"},{"pi